---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout>
    <!-- alt det her er det der bliver til <slot /> i Layout.astro -->
    
    
    <h1 class="overskrift">Schedule for 2024</h1> 

    <div class="underrubrik">
        <p>Explore the develeopment and challenges in the UX industry as a perceived and experienced by 
            UX professionals of different backgrounds and specialitied.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    
    
    <button class="knap">
        <p>March 21 - Day 2</p>
    </button>


    <button class="knap_2">
        <p>March 20 - Day 1</p>
    </button>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="tid_1">
            <p>9:30-9:40</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tid_2">
            <p>9:40–10:10</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tid_3">
            <p>10:10–10:40</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tid_4">
            <p>10:40–12:00</p> 
        </div>
        <div class="tid_5">
            <p>12:00–13:00</p> 
        </div>
        <div class="tid_6">
            <p>13:00–17:00</p>
        </div>

        
            <div class="tekst_1">
                <p>Welcome by Helle Martens</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tekst_2">
                <p>Ethical Design by Mansi Gupta
                    A talk about Ethical Design, and the many ways it can be incorporated into the work process.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tekst_3">
                <p>A Systems Thinking Approach to Designer Ethics by Laura Yarrow
                    What is Systems Thinking, and how can we use this approach to understand the impact we have as designers on society and the world.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tekst_4">
                <p>The Cynic’s Guide to Designing For Social Good by Rebecca Rae-Evans
                    This talk is all about what not to do when designing for social good. What works, what doesn’t work, and what makes Rebecca scream into a pillow with rage at the end of the working day.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="tekst_5">
                <p>Lunch break</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tekst_6">
                <p>Discussing Influence and Designing For Good by Don Norman
                    We invite you to join us for an interactive discussion about the theme, Influence and Designing For Good, with Don Norman
                </p>
            </div>
        

    </div>


    <!-- slot slut -->
</Layout>



